                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Guide</p>
                  <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">
                    Documenting a new component
                  </h2>
                  <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-6 text-muted-foreground">
                    Use <code>docs/component-documentation-guide.md</code> as the
                    handoff prompt for another AI agent. The short version: add the
                    component under <code>src/components/ui</code>, import its
                    source with <code>?raw</code>, add it to navigation, then
                    include preview, usage, props, copy, download, and hidden
                    source code sections.
                  </p>
